GENERAL NOTES
-----------------
HOW TO RUN PROGRAM, JUST DOUBLE CLICK THE PROGRAM .EXE
THE PROGRAM IS ABLE TO HANDLE ANY TYPE OF MICROWAVE DATA. AS LONG AS IT HAS X AND Y COLUMNS. IT WAS DESIGNED FOR CAVITY BASED, BUT HAS BEEN TESTED WITH LARGE AMOUNTS OF DATA, E.G. MMWAVE-DATA(CYCLOBUTENONE), CF2I2 (CHIRPED PULSE), AND 1,1-DIIODOETHANE(CAVITY), TRICHLOROACETONITRILE(CAVITY)
BUTTONS IN THE PROGRAM
LOAD EXP (TOP) - LOADS EXPERIMENTAL SPECTRA 
LOAD PRED(BOTTOM) - LOADS .FREQ (PREDICTION SPECTRA) (MAY EVEN BE ABLE TO LOAD THE .CAT FILE FROM SPCAT)
-----------------
USAGE
MAGNIFYING GLASS IS FOR ZOOMING IN, BACK ARROW IS FOR GOING BACK A STEP, FOWARD ARROW GOING BACK TO INITIAL STOP.
RIGHT CLICK - CLICK ONCE GIVES LINE, DOUBLE CLICK-PRODUCES ANOTHER LINE AND GIVES DOPPLER SPLITTING ALONG WITH CENTER FREQUENCY
LEFT CLICK -USERS MOVEMENTS
